90
00:05:10,680 --> 00:05:13,980
These are things that can make us sick if we don't make them cold.

91
00:05:14,339 --> 00:05:14,680
Exactly.

92
00:05:15,259 --> 00:05:16,920
So those are the two words.

93
00:05:17,160 --> 00:05:25,620
